ding-libs
------------------------------------------
'DING is not GNU' helper libraries for SSSD and FreeIPA

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libdhash-devel-0.7.0-1bl1
  libdhash1-0.7.0-1bl1
  libiconv2-1.17-1
  libini_config-devel-0.7.0-1bl1
  libini_config8-0.7.0-1bl1
  libintl8-0.22.5-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  check-0.15.2-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gettext-devel-0.22.5-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/SSSD/ding-libs

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/SSSD/ding-libs/archive/refs/tags/0.7.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ding-libs-0.7.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ding-libs-0.7.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ding-libs-0.7.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ding-libs-0.7.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdhash1-0.7.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libdhash-devel-0.7.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libini_config8-0.7.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libini_config-devel-0.7.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ding-libs)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ding-libs.README
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/README

(libdhash1)
  /usr/bin/cygdhash-1.dll

(libdhash-devel)
  /usr/include/dhash.h
  /usr/lib/libdhash.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/dhash.pc
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/README.dhash
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/examples/dhash_example.c
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/examples/dhash_test.c

(libini_config8)
  /usr/bin/cygini_config-8.dll

(libini_config-devel)
  /usr/include/ini_configmod.h
  /usr/include/ini_configobj.h
  /usr/include/ref_array.h
  /usr/lib/libini_config.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ini_config.pc
  /usr/share/doc/ding-libs/README.ref_array

